descriptionHTML: Custom Made Home Design Game I want a game like :Episode - Choose Your Story ( https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.episodeinteractive.android.catalog ) or Romance Fate: Stories and Choices( https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.saiyun.avgchapters.episodestories.romance ) for Android Platform on the first stage. The game must • have quality designs not sketch designs • A storyline in order to engage with the players and also levels ( more info will be discuss on Fiverr and on meeting ) • In-App for items, jewelry, clothes, watches, shoes and Game Gems ; Game and Day Pass or Week Pass ( with these Day Pass or Week Pass we will give to the player the chance to earn x5 times more gems if they watch Rewards Ads – this is an idea, we can craft it later on ) • Rewards Ads ( players must watch Ads In order to win Gems in the game which can be converter in Item ) • In Game Ads ( Interstitial Ads after 5 levels ) • The game must have at least 25 Levels and a storyline • We need Push Notification in order to keep the players active every day, we can use OneSignal Plugin – I will pay for the OneSignal Plugin License ) • We need after 3 levels to introduce a pop-up with Review Us on Google Play and we will give each user who review the game in Google Play ( the prize for review will be a One Day Pass ) • We need to think about player retention, in order no to leave the game after one day, we need to keep them engage with the game as much as we can • Source Code • Animations • Design • The game must have a backstory when the player will play for the first time in order to introduce it into the game and also a trail in order to know the buttons and how to play the game • Developer must help me to upload the game on Google Play Store
